<h2 id="development">Development</h2>

<p>To set up your environment to develop this theme, clone this repo, then run <code>bundle install</code>. To test the theme, run <code>bundle exec jekyll serve</code> and open your browser at <code>http://localhost:4000</code>. Add pages, documents, data, etc. like normal to test the themeâ€™s contents. As you make modifications, your site will regenerate and you should see the changes in the browser after a refresh, just like normal.</p>

